social_posts.post_text:
And now here we are at this “sad conclusion.” 💔

Happy closing to @arvadacenter ‘s production of #BeautyAndTheBeast
✨🥀✨🐗✨

This is without a doubt the most generous, beautiful, and bravest bunch of artists I have worked with in a long time. It was a pleasure to share the stage with all of you. I pray the people I work with in the future are able to meet the standard you have all just set. 

Thank you to Director @kmofoco and Choreographer @jess1867 for reminding us all that theatre can be bold, daring, and above all…safe. Any theatre lucky enough to have the two of you will forever be changed.  The front of house producing staff, creators, designers, tech, musicians lead by #JordanOrtman, volunteers, and everyone involved here are a treasure. To say I will miss you all is an understatement. Share your joy and light everywhere you go friends. They are so lucky to have you. 
✨🍀✨

#ArtSaves #ArtChanges #ArtIsAllAround
The perfect way to end this year. 🥰
Goodbye #Denver & Hello #Orlando !

To work in a space where you are completely free and safe at all times to create, be vulnerable, and be your most authentic weird self is a gift. 

.

To not need to search for humanity on and offstage because everyone around you is selflessly giving and devoted to their craft is a gift. 

.

To be recognized by the @coloradotheatreguild for a piece that is so personal to me and would not have been possible without every Artist involved is a gift. 

Thank you.

I would like to say a special thanks for the amazing entertainment on these 2 fantastic cruises being Fiji and New Zealand. Its been an absolute pleasure to meet the vocalist, dancers, hosts, and many more on what they do for all of us.

The amazing shows what they do for us from Sweet soul music, to the classical Encore show and my personal favourite, Colours of the world just absolutely amazing to see the amount of time and effort what these people do for us in their shows.

I would also like to say a special thanks to @officialmichaelcarrasco who has been an absolute legend from his vocals and just being a great person. Thanks for inspiring me to continue on loving musical theater, love hearing your voice time and time again, thank you very much!!!

Its been absolutely amazing watching these shows and keep shinning on!!!
